## Limitations

The report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the potential bias in sources advocating for veterans' rights. Additionally, the complexity of immigration laws and individual case circumstances means that the findings may not capture all nuances of the deportation process. Further research could include interviews with affected veterans and legal experts to provide a more comprehensive understanding of the issue.